==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Longing
<hw>Long"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An eager desire; a
craving; a morbid appetite; an earnest wish; an aspiration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Put on my crown; I have⟦br⟧
immortal <qex>longings</qex> in me.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Longingly</ent>⟦br⟧
